<app-shell>
  <view class="screen">
    <view class="screen__stack">
      <hero-card
        eyebrow="S11 Treehole"
        title="匿名树洞广场"
        summary="这里展示已公开的匿名表达。你可以用预设互动传递支持，也可以写下一条自己的心情。"
        tone="brand"
      />

      <view wx:if="{{feedDisabled}}" class="surface-card surface-card--warm">
        <view class="eyebrow">当前不可用</view>
        <view class="section-subtitle">你尚未开放危机干预授权，因此不能进入树洞发布链路</view>
        <view class="body-text">
          你仍然可以继续完成问卷与查看报告；若之后开放授权，树洞入口会自动恢复可用。
        </view>
        <view class="button-stack treehole-page__actions">
          <secondary-button label="返回首页" bind:tap="handleBackHome" />
        </view>
      </view>

      <block wx:else>
        <view wx:if="{{deleteNotice}}" class="status-banner status-banner--success">
          {{deleteNotice}}
        </view>

        <view class="surface-card surface-card--soft">
          <view class="treehole-page__section-head">
            <view>
              <view class="eyebrow">Public Feed</view>
              <view class="section-subtitle">只展示匿名昵称、头像和脱敏正文</view>
            </view>
            <view class="helper-text">不开放评论和私信</view>
          </view>
          <view class="body-text">
            广场里的每条内容都以匿名形式公开呈现。互动只保留“抱抱 / 点亮 / 陪伴”三种支持反馈，避免讨论区失控和身份暴露。
          </view>
          <view class="treehole-page__metric-row">
            <view class="treehole-page__metric">
              <view class="treehole-page__metric-label">公开帖子</view>
              <view class="treehole-page__metric-value">{{metrics.publicCount}}</view>
            </view>
            <view class="treehole-page__metric">
              <view class="treehole-page__metric-label">我的帖子</view>
              <view class="treehole-page__metric-value">{{metrics.myCount}}</view>
            </view>
            <view class="treehole-page__metric">
              <view class="treehole-page__metric-label">支持反馈</view>
              <view class="treehole-page__metric-value">{{metrics.supportCount}}</view>
            </view>
          </view>
          <view class="button-stack treehole-page__actions">
            <primary-button label="发布一条匿名心情" bind:tap="handleCreateTap" />
          </view>
        </view>

        <view wx:if="{{loadError}}" class="status-banner status-banner--error">
          {{loadError}}
        </view>

        <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="surface-card">
          <view class="eyebrow">加载中</view>
          <view class="section-subtitle">正在同步树洞广场</view>
          <view class="body-text">请稍候，系统正在加载已公开的匿名内容与最新互动状态。</view>
        </view>

        <view wx:elif="{{posts.length}}" class="treehole-page__feed-list">
          <treehole-post-card
            wx:for="{{posts}}"
            wx:key="postId"
            anonymousName="{{item.anonymousName}}"
            anonymousAvatarKey="{{item.anonymousAvatarKey}}"
            relativeTime="{{item.relativeTime}}"
            content="{{item.content}}"
          >
            <view slot="head-extra" class="chip-row">
              <view wx:if="{{item.isMine}}" class="chip">我的帖子</view>
              <view class="chip chip--muted">{{item.totalReactionCount}} 条支持</view>
            </view>

            <view class="treehole-page__reaction-row">
              <reaction-chip
                wx:for="{{item.reactions}}"
                wx:for-item="reaction"
                wx:key="reactionType"
                label="{{reaction.label}}"
                count="{{reaction.count}}"
                active="{{reaction.reactedByMe}}"
                disabled="{{reaction.busy}}"
                data-post-id="{{item.postId}}"
                data-reaction-type="{{reaction.reactionType}}"
                bind:tap="handleReactionTap"
              />
            </view>

            <view class="treehole-page__post-foot">
              <view class="helper-text">
                {{item.isMine ? '这条帖子来自你自己。可进入详情查看完整内容并执行删除。' : '当前阶段只开放预设互动，不开放评论和私信。'}}
              </view>
              <view
                class="treehole-page__detail-link"
                data-post-id="{{item.postId}}"
                bindtap="handlePostTap"
              >
                {{item.detailLinkLabel}}
              </view>
            </view>
          </treehole-post-card>
        </view>

        <view wx:elif="{{!loadError}}" class="surface-card surface-card--warm">
          <view class="treehole-page__empty-state">
            <view class="treehole-page__empty-mark">匿</view>
            <view class="section-subtitle">广场还没有公开帖子</view>
            <view class="body-text">
              你可以先发布一条自己的匿名心情。公开前会自动去除手机号和邮箱等明显联系方式。
            </view>
            <view class="button-stack">
              <primary-button label="写下第一条树洞" bind:tap="handleCreateTap" />
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view wx:if="{{loadError}}" class="button-stack">
          <secondary-button label="重新加载广场" bind:tap="handleRetryLoad" />
        </view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>
</app-shell>
